utilities

Class Constants

  • java.lang.Object
    • utilities.Constants

  • public class Constants
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains all the constants for the application.

    This method was created for easy access to files and essential, frequently-used constants throughout the program, such as screen dimensions.

    Since:
    1.0, 5/17/2022 Modification on 5/26/2022
